♪Mist rises in swirls♪

666
00:39:35,871 --> 00:39:39,041
♪She steps onto the battlefield♪

667
00:39:39,321 --> 00:39:43,141
♪No distraction is allowed♪

668
00:39:44,481 --> 00:39:47,541
♪A touch of love, a trace of hate♪

669
00:39:47,801 --> 00:39:50,311
♪No need to question♪

670
00:39:52,201 --> 00:39:55,181
♪The truth and falsehood♪

671
00:39:55,181 --> 00:39:58,271
♪Needs to be discerned♪

672
00:39:59,031 --> 00:40:02,371
♪Seeking warmth in peril♪

673
00:40:02,371 --> 00:40:06,711
♪Only to be mocked as naive♪

674
00:40:06,831 --> 00:40:10,181
♪War drums sound, beacons flare♪

675
00:40:10,181 --> 00:40:14,051
♪Who can break free♪

676
00:40:14,491 --> 00:40:16,951
♪She is willing to become a blade♪

677
00:40:16,951 --> 00:40:18,901
♪Moving forward without retreat♪

678
00:40:18,901 --> 00:40:22,181
♪Charging into this lonely fortress♪

679
00:40:22,181 --> 00:40:24,751
♪Even in a fateful clash♪

680
00:40:24,751 --> 00:40:26,571
♪With eyes stained with blood♪

681
00:40:26,571 --> 00:40:29,821
♪She holds no grudge♪

682
00:40:30,031 --> 00:40:32,391
♪She does not trust fate♪

683
